<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
    <head>
        <title></title>
        <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
        <style type="text/css">
            body{
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                font-size: 12px;
            }
            *{
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
            }
            .main{
                
                margin: 20px 10px;
                
            }
            .list{
                margin-top: 10px;
                border-radius: 5px; 
                background: #F2F2F2;
                padding: 10px;
                padding-right: 0;
            }
            .list .jwgz{
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
            .list .info{
                margin: 10px 10px 10px 0;
                padding: 10px;
                border: 1px solid #DEDEDE;
                
            }
            .list .info .pubaccount{
                font-size: 14px;
            }
            .list .info .wxaccount{
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
            .list .info .content{
                margin-top: 10px;
            }
            .clear{
                clear: both;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        
        <div class="main">
            
            <div class="list">
                <div class="logo"><img src="Uploads{$data.qrcode}" width="150" height="150" /></div>
                <div class="jwgz">
                    加为关注的方法：<br>
                    1、点击（需长按）二维码保存至图库，启动微信扫一扫，从相册选择二维码关注。<br>
                    2、点击（需长按）公众帐号复制，启动微信选择朋友们-添加朋友-查找微信公众帐号关注。
                </div>
                <div class="info">
                    
                    <div class="pubaccount">{$data.pubaccount}</div>
                    <div class="wxaccount">微信帐号：{$data.wxaccount}</div>
                    <div class="content">帐号介绍：<br>
                        {$data.content}
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
            
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
